channel.title: Comments on: Level Up! Series – Off to a Good Start

item.title: By: Ben
item.dc:creator: Ben
item.description: Haha. Well, from an early age, my reading speed has always been pretty fast. I will be the first to admit that I can't remember everything after reading it only once, but I can process most of it very quickly, which is the most important part for book reviews. =)
